posts.title: Best Router for Home
posts.text: Best Router for HomeNETGEAR R6700 Nighthawk AC1750 Dual Band Smart WiFi Router, Gigabit Ethernet (R6700) I definitely recommend this product. Initially bought a router for about $30, but it simply would not function well. So I had to add another 15-20 dollars to my budget and bought this one and it really works nice.
